Name: libGHF 
Description:
   A General Purpose Binary Modification Library
License: GPL License 
  <http://opensource.org/licenses/gpl-license.php>
  Copyright 2006 *nixCoders team

Compilation:
  It's simple: 
  For production build 
     $ make libghf.a RELEASE=1
  For debug build
     $ make libghf.a

  Doing 'make' alone builds a test library as well.

Todo:
  - X86_64 support :p
